    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It runs like a dream and has been my trusty companion, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is looking for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to chat! \u2728",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit boasts a documented Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, eschewing the SMG for a more tactile engagement. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure internal longevity. The chassis is stabilized with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded bushings, mitigating common fatigue points. Power is delivered to the tarmac via a factory Variable M Differential Lock, providing exceptional lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain dialed-in for precision cornering and linear throttle response.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Reliable performance. Clean interior. Minor exterior wear. Recent maintenance complete. Ready for road.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes an excellent balance between daily utility and premium comfort. The exterior paint maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals minor, typical road wear like small stone chips on the front fascia and a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful ownership. The body panels are straight and free of significant dents. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery remains supple and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's side bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in strong standing; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a complete logbook included. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a brake inspection, confirming that the pads and rotors have significant life left. The tires are a matching set of Michelins with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a solid, well-cared-for example that is ready for immediate turn-key enjoyment.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, a testament to consistent care and engineering excellence. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure optimal mechanical performance and structural integrity. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience for those who prioritize reliability and long-term value. This is a premier selection for the discerning buyer seeking a high-caliber automobile in its class.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this awesome ride! It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape, just waiting for its next big adventure with you. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road immediately. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and feels even better to drive, this is the one! I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional volumetric efficiency via its individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is bolstered by a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounting points, addressing critical chassis rigidity. Suspension geometry is maintained through refreshed bushings, ensuring the factory-spec limited-slip differential puts power down effectively through the apex. While the exterior displays minor road-wear consistent with spirited use, the powertrain remains a benchmark of M-Division precision, offering a tactile 8,000 RPM redline and a linear torque curve that modern turbocharged engines cannot replicate.",
      "price": 32500.0,
